

--> to compile kernel source code

sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=/opt/poky-atmel/2.4.4/sysroots/x86_64-pokysdk-linux/usr/bin/arm-poky-linux-gnueabi/arm-poky-linux-gnueabi-  uImage dtbs LOADADDR=0x80008000 

--> compile the dts file

sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=/opt/poky-atmel/2.4.4/sysroots/x86_64-pokysdk-linux/usr/bin/arm-poky-linux-gnueabi/arm-poky-linux-gnueabi-  at91-sama5d2_com3.dtb
